\c 14
\s VaIsraeri vanomukira Jehovha
\p
\v 1 Zvino ungano yose yakasimudza ndokupa inzwi rayo\x + Gen. 45.2.\x*; vanhu ndokuchema usiku ihwohwo\x + 11.4.\x*.
\v 2 Nevana vaIsraeri vose vakagunun'unira Mozisi naAroni\x + 14.27,29,36. Eki. 15.24; 16.2; 17.3. Num. 16.41. Josh. 9.18. Map. 106.25.\x*; ungano yose ndokuti kwavari: Dai takafira munyika yeEgipita; kana: Dai takafira murenje rino\x + 14.27,28,29.\x*!
\v 3 Zvino sei Jehovha akatiuisa kunyika ino, tigowa nemunondo? Vakadzi vedu nevana vedu vachava vadzimbiwa. Hazvingavi zvakanaka kwatiri kuti tidzokere kuEgipita here?
\v 4 Zvino vakati umwe kune umwe: Ngatigadzei mutungamiriri\x + Neh. 9.17.\x*, tigodzokera kuEgipita\x + Det. 17.16. Mab. 7.39.\x*.
\v 5 Mozisi naAroni ndokuwa nezviso zvavo pamberi peboka rose reungano yevana vaIsraeri\x + 16.4,22.\x*.
\p
\v 6 NaJoshua mwanakomana waNuni, naKarebhu mwanakomana waJefune, veavo vakanoshora nyika, vakabvarura nguvo dzavo.
\v 7 Ndokutaura kuungano yose yevana vaIsraeri vachiti: Nyika yatakagura mairi kuishora, inyika yakanaka kwazvo-kwazvo\x + 13.27. Det. 1.25.\x*.
\v 8 Kana Jehovha achifara nesu, ipapo achatiisa kunyika iyi\x + 2 Zvak. 15.26; 22.20. 1 Madz. 10.9. Map. 18.19; 22.8. Isa. 62.4.\x*, ndokuipa kwatiri; nyika inoyerera mukaka neuchi\x + 13.27. Eki. 3.8.\x*.
\v 9 Koga musapandukira Jehovha\x + Josh. 22.16,18,19,29.\x*, uye imwi musatya vanhu venyika iyo\x + Det. 7.18; 20.3.\x*, nokuti \add ivo\add* izvekudya zvedu\x + 24.8.\x*; mumvuri wavo wabva kwavari, uye Jehovha anesu, musavatya\x + Gen. 48.21. Det. 20.1,4; 31. 6.\x*.
\v 10 Asi ungano yose yakataura kuvataka nemabwe\x + Eki. 17.4.\x*. Kubwinya kwaJehovha ndokuonekwa mutende rekusangana kuvana vaIsraeri vese\x + Eki. 16.7,10. Rev. 9.23. Num. 16.19,42; 20.6.\x*.
\p
\v 11 Zvino Jehovha wakati kuna Mozisi: Kusvika rinhi vanhu ava vachindizvidza\x + 14.23; 16.30.\x*? Uye kusvika rinhi vasinganditendi nezvishamiso zvose zvandakaita pakati pavo\x + Det. 1.32; 9.23. Map. 78.22,32; 106.24. Joh. 12.37. VaHeb. 3.18.\x*?
\v 12 Ndichavarova nedenda, nekuvatorera nhaka\x + Eki. 15.9,24.\x*, ndikuite rudzi rukuru rune simba pana ivo\x + Eki. 32.10.\x*.
\p
\v 13 Mozisi ndokuti kuna Jehovha: Zvino VaEgipita vacha\add zvi\add*nzwa; nokuti makakwidza vanhu ava pakati pavo nesimba renyu\x + Eki. 32.12. Det. 9.26,27,28; 32.27. Eze. 20.9,14. Map. 106.23.\x*;
\v 14 uye vachaudza vagari venyika ino. Vakanzwa kuti imwi Jehovha muri pakati pevanhu ava; nokuti imwi Jehovha munoonekwa chiso nechiso\x + Eki. 15.14; Josh. 2.9,10; 5.1.\x*, uye gore renyu rinomira pamusoro pavo, nemwi munovatungamirira masikati mushongwe yegore, nepausiku mushongwe yemoto\x + Eki. 13.21.\x*.
\v 15 Zvino mukauraya vanhu ava semunhu umwe, ndudzi dzakanzwa mukurumbira wenyu dzichataura dzichiti:
\v 16 Nokuti Jehovha wakakonewa kuisa vanhu ava kunyika yaakavapikira, saka akavauraya murenje\x + Det. 9.28. Josh. 7.9.\x*.
\v 17 Zvino ikozvino ndinokumbira kuti simba raIshe wangu rive guru, sezvamakataura, muchiti:
\v 18 Jehovha anononoka kutsamwa, uye mukuru panyasha, achikanganwira zvakaipa nekudarika, asi haangatongoregeri \add ane mhosva\x + Eki. 34.6,7. Map. 103.8; 145.8. Jona 4.2.\x*\add*, anotsiva kuipa kwemadzibaba pavana, kusvika ku\add rudzi\add* rwechitatu nerwechina\x + Eki. 20.5.\x*.
\v 19 Ndinokumbira, kanganwirai zvakaipa zvevanhu ava\x + Eki. 34.9.\x* seukuru hwenyasha dzenyu\x + Map. 106.45.\x*, uye sezvamakakanganwira vanhu ava kubva Egipita kusvika ikozvino\x + Map. 78.38.\x*.
\p
\v 20 Jehovha ndokuti: Ndakanganwira maererano neinzwi rako\x + Map. 106.23. Jak. 5.16. 1 Joh. 5.16.\x*.
\v 21 Asi zvirokwazvo, ndichirarama, nyika yose ichazara nekubwinya kwaJehovha\x + Map. 72.19.\x*.
\v 22 Nokuti varume ava vose vakaona kubwinya kwangu nezviratidzo zvangu zvandakaita muEgipita nemurenje, vakandiidza\x + Det. 1.35. Map. 95.11; 106.26. VaHeb. 3.17,18.\x* kagumi aka, uye vakasateerera inzwi rangu\x + Gen.\x*,
\v 23 zvirokwazvo havachaoni nyika yandakapikira madzibaba avo; uye hakuna umwe wevakandizvidza achaiona\x + 32.11. Eze. 20.15.\x*.
\v 24 Asi muranda wangu Karebhu\x + 13.6.\x*, nokuti umwe mweya waiva anaye, ndokunditevera zvakazara, ndichamupinza munyika maakambopinda; nevana vake vachadya nhaka yayo\x + 32.11,12. Det. 1.36. Josh. 14.9.\x*.
\v 25 Zvino VaAmareki\x + 14.43,45;13.29.\x* neVaKenani\x + 14.43,45;13.29.\x* vaigara mumupata uyo; mangwana dzokai, imwi mubve muende kurenje nenzira yeGungwa Dzvuku\x + Det. 1.40.\x*.
\p
\v 26 Zvino Jehovha wakataura kuna Mozisi nekuna Aroni achiti:
\v 27 Kusvika rinhi \add ndakatakura\add* ungano iyi yakaipa inondigunun'unira? Ndakanzwa kugunun'una kwevana vaIsraeri kwavakandigunun'unira nako\x + Eki. 16.7,12.\x*.
\v 28 Uti kwavari: Ndichirarama\x + 14.21,23; 26.65.\x*, anoreva Jehovha, zvirokwazvo sezvamakataura munzeve dzangu, ndizvo zvandichakuitirai\x + 14.2.\x*.
\v 29 Zvitunha zvenyu zvichawira murenje rino; nevose vakaverengwa venyu, zvichienderana neuwandu hwenyu hwese, kubva pazera remakore makumi maviri zvichikwira, vakandigunun'unira\x + 1.45; 26.64. Det. 1.35.\x*,
\v 30 zvirokwazvo, imwi hamuchapindi munyika yandapikira kukugarisai mairi, kunze kwaKarebhu mwanakomana waJefune, naJoshua mwanakomana waNuni\x + 14.6,38; 13.6.\x*.
\v 31 Asi vana venyu vamakati vachadzimbiwa, ndivo vandichapinza\x + 14.3. Det. 1.39.\x*; uye vachaziva nyika yamakaramba\x + Map. 106.24.\x*.
\v 32 Asi imwi, zvitunha zvenyu zvichawira murenje rino\x + 14.29,33. VaHeb. 3.17.\x*.
\v 33 Zvino vana venyu vachava vafudzi murenje\x + 32.13; Map. 107.40.\x* makore makumi mana\x + Map. 95.10; Det. 2.14.\x*, vakatakura ufeve hwenyu, kusvika zvitunha zvenyu zvaparadzwa murenje\x + Eze. 23.35.\x*.
\v 34 Maererano neuwandu hwemazuva amakashora nawo nyika\x + 13.25.\x*, mazuva makumi mana, zuva pagore\x + Eze. 4.6.\x*, zuva pagore, muchatakura kuipa kwenyu, makore makumi mana\x + Rev. 5.1.\x*, mugoziva kufuratira kwangu.
\v 35 Ini Jehovha ndakataura: Zvirokwazvo ndichazviita\x + 23.19.\x* kuungano iyi yose yakaipa, yakaungana kupikisana neni; murenje rino vachaparadzwa, uye vachafirapo\x + 14.27; 26.65. 1 VaKori. 10.5.\x*.
\v 36 Zvino varume Mozisi vaakatuma kunoshora nyika, vakadzoka ndokuita kuti ungano yose imugunun'unire, nekuuisa nhema \add dzakaipa\add* pamusoro penyika iyo\x + 13.32.\x*,
\v 37 avawo varume vakauya nenhema dzakaipa maererano nenyika iyo vakafa nedenda pamberi paJehovha\x + 1 VaKori. 10.10. VaHeb. 3.10,17. Jud. 5.\x*.
\v 38 Asi Joshua mwanakomana waNuni naKarebhu mwanakomana waJefune vakararama pavarume avo vakanoshora nyika\x + 13.8,16.\x*.
\v 39 Zvino Mozisi wakareva mashoko awa kuvana vaIsraeri vose; vanhu ndokuungudza kwazvo\x + Eki. 33.4.\x*.
\p
\v 40 Zvino vakamuka mangwanani-ngwanani, vakakwira kunhongonya yegomo, vachiti: Tarirai, tiri \add pano\add*, uye tichakwira kunzvimbo Jehovha yaakataura, nokuti tatadza\x + Det. 1.41.\x*.
\v 41 Mozisi ndokuti: Munodarikirei murairo waJehovha? Nokuti hazvingabudiriri\x + 2 Makor. 24.20. Num. 14.25.\x*.
\v 42 Musakwira, nokuti Jehovha haasi pakati penyu; kuti murege kurohwa pamberi pevavengi venyu\x + Det. 1.42.\x*.
\v 43 Nokuti VaAmareki neVaKenani varipo mberi kwenyu; zvino muchawa nemunondo, nokuti makadzoka pakutevera Jehovha, naizvozvo Jehovha haachavi nemwi\x + 14.25,45; 13.29.\x*.
\v 44 Asi vakazvikudza kukwira kunhongonya yegomo\x + Det. 1.43.\x*; asi areka yesungano yaJehovha naMozisi hazvina kubuda mukati memusasa\x + 1 Zvak. 4.3.\x*.
\v 45 Ipapo VaAmareki neVaKenani vaiva vagere mugomo iro vakaburuka, ndokuvarova\x + 14.43. Det. 1.44.\x* nekuvadzingirira kusvika kuHorima\x + 21.3; Vato. 1.17.\x*.